	'unsigned char *'.
	(mips_receive_packet): Remove cast to 'unsigned char *'.
	(mips_load_srec): Use bfd_byte.
	(pmon_makeb64, pmon_zeroset): Make 'chksum' parameter unsigned.
	(pmon_checkset): Make 'value' parameter unsigned.
